description:
Read and write NFC Tags for TonUINO
This app simplifies writing of NFC tags for the open source TonUINO DIY music box.
More information about TonUINO can be found at https://www.voss.earth/tonuino

This app will only work if the device supports NFC.

It also shows the content of written TonUINO NFC tags, and allows for simple copying or changing.
